data.description: Charming spacious 2BD 2B w/large living room and den, located on a quiet corner lot of a dead-end street. Mature trees shade the fenced backyard creating a private atmosphere around the lighted patio and Koi pond, also great for entertaining. Also included are 2 storage building and a greenhouse. Easy to enjoy indoor and outdoor living.
